A Muvhango-type of war has broken out between the family of the late Motswako megastar Hip Hop Pantsula (HHP) and his son's gogo over the custody of the teenager. Sunday World can exclusively reveal that Mapule Rachel Khanye has applied for a court order that would declare her the legal guardian of the 15-year-old boy. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD